st)|John Clarke]], [[Nicholas Papademetriou]] || Black Comedy / Romance || [https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0101692/ IMDb]\n|-\n| ''Deep Dive'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''Fatal Sky'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Father (1990 film)|Father]]'' || John Power || [[Max von Sydow]], [[Julia Blake]], [[Carol Drinkwater]], [[Steve Jacobs]] || Drama / War || Entered into the [[17th Moscow International Film Festival]]\n|-\n| ''Flowers by Request'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''Friday on My Mind'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Golden Braid]]'' || [[Paul Cox (director)|Paul Cox]] || [[Chris Haywood]], [[Gosia Dobrowolska]], [[Paul Chubb]], [[Norman Kaye]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Green Card (film)|Green Card]]'' || [[Peter Weir]] || [[G\u00e9rard Depardieu]], [[Andie MacDowell]] || Romantic comedy || Won Oscar & Golden Globe, +1 win, +3 nominations\n|-\n| ''[[Harbour Beat]]'' || [[David Elfick]] || [[John Hannah (actor)|John Hannah]], [[Gary Day (actor)|Gary Day]], [[Tony Poli]], [[Angie Milliken]], [[Peta Toppano]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Heaven Tonight (film)|Heaven Tonight]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''In Too Deep'' || || [[Hugo Race]], Santha Press, [[Rebekah Elmaloglou]], [[John Flaus]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Jigsaw_(1989_film)|Jigsaw]]'' || [[Marc Gracie]] || [[Rebecca Gibney]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[A Kink in the Picasso]]'' || [[Marc Gracie]] || [[Peter O'Brien (actor)|Peter O'Brien]], [[Jane Clifton]], [[Jon Finlayson]], [[Andrew Daddo]] || || [https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099940/ IMDb]\n|-\n| ''The Man in the Blue and White Holden'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''Man Without Pigs'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Nirvana Street Murder]]'' || [[Aleksi Vellis]] || [[Mark Little (Australian actor)|Mark Little]], [[Ben Mendelsohn]], [[Mary Coustas]] || Comedy || [https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0102539/ IMDb]\n|-\n| ''[[The Phantom Horseman (1990 film)|The Phantom Horseman]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''Phobia'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''Plead Guilty, Get a Bond'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Quigley Down Under]]'' || [[Simon Wincer]] || [[Tom Selleck]], [[Alan Rickman]